snippet.description:

Director : Ben Rayner (@benrayner)
Executive Producer: Domenic Palermo
DOP : Joe Bressler (@joebressler)
Gaffer : Dom Bozzi (@dominickbozzi)
Grip : Devan Davies Wood (@devan_dw)
AC : Lucas Hrabal (@lucas_hraval.dp)
Stylist : @ Cece Liu (@cc_looo)
Editor : Mike Martinez (@mike____martinez)
Actors : Dom Potter (@y.uck___) and Sharyl (@shar.yl)
PA : Aaron Heard (@aaronheard_)
Shot at 718 Studios (@718studiosnyc)

Produced, Engineered, Mixed, and Mastered by @willyipmusic
Additional Production by Domenic Palermo
Assisted Engineering by Hank Byerly
Recorded at Studio 4 Recording in Conshohocken, PA.
Composed by Domenic Palermo, Kyle Kimball, Aaron Heard, and Doyle Martin
Additional Auxiliary Percussion by Will Yip
Violin, Viola, and Cello by @shelleyweissmusic

Amber Gambler

Thick as thieves 
Nickel and diming
Not nine to fiving
Grasping at their straws
A second bite of the cherry?
On the contrary 
We were in dire straights
Moonlight requisition 
Done by mirrors

Head for Easy street 

That's everything I've got to say

Loaded to the gills
I call shotgun
Let’s cut to the chase
Pedal 
To the medal 
Amber gambler
Got us in a pinch 

That's everything I've got to say

Head nor tail
A lost ball in the high weeds
Head eats tail
It’s always clear as mud
It’s always clear as mud

Bed and 
breakfast 
23 and 1 again
Fly kites to a friend
Count sheep
With one eye open
With a loss for words 
Ok?

That’s everything I’ve got to say
